Package: rmonad
Title: A monadic system for pipeline development
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Zebulun Arendsee
Maintainer: Zebulun Arendsee <arendsee@iastate.edu>
URL: https://github.com/arendsee/rmonad
BugReports: https://github.com/arendsee/rmonad/issues
Description:
    Rmonad offers monadic pipelines with nuanced error handling, access to
    intermediate results, and automatic benchmarking. It complements, rather
    than competes with, non-monadic pipeline programs like magrittr or pipeR.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    magrittr,
    methods
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    tibble
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
